Germ was left on a surface. It was going to be warm and unwelcoming soon. Germ only had minutes to find a host to replicate.
This was germs first time out of the original host. A sneeze booted them out without warning.

The germ continued to sit there on the table, reflecting on its past.
Suddenly, something huge came upon the germ, about to squish it. This was the germ's chance to find a new host!
